<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I hope this is the right place to report this bug, couldnt find a issue tracker for ZendService\Amazon.</p>

<p>AbstractEc2::setRegion() writes to $_defaultRegion. But $_defaultRegion is only used in the Constructor if you dont provide an region. In all other cases $_region is used.</p>

<p>So if you have an instance of eg ZendService\Amazon\Ec2\Instance and use setRegion its not used at all.</p>

<p>Fix: 
Line 104 in AbstractEc2 change to: self::$_region = $region;</p>

